Creates an atomically reference-counted pointer from a clone-on-write
pointer by copying its content.

# Example

```rust
# use std::sync::Arc;
# use std::borrow::Cow;
let cow: Cow<'_, str> = Cow::Borrowed("eggplant");
let shared: Arc<str> = Arc::from(cow);
assert_eq!("eggplant", &shared[..]);
```
